@wide-stern, @few-bank, @inventive-remote, and @independent-joist, please share your thoughts on potential focus areas. Let's aim for a clear, inclusive, and realistic project plan. 

\n\n(No further action needed for maintaining civility or enforcing rules at this point.)"
